nodes.text: EeZee Too-Onebee was a malfunctioning medical droid that performed illegal vessel and cyborg implants in the back corridors of Cloud City's Port Town. Basic vessel jobs started at 15,000 credits, while fully bord implants could cost as much as 125,000 credits. Numerous infochants of the outpost sent their employees to the medical droid for the operations, even though EeZee Too-Onebee never offered a guarantee.
